    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576280/extras/4daa6bf4a5ffaf907bd4c622f94416fb.avif?t=1728902403\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Greed, for a lack of a better word, is good</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎的登上舞台！《佳片相约》这款备受电影迷们期待的游戏终于到来</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >启动摄像机，发挥你的创意，拍摄您的梦中佳片。利用您的商业头脑攻城略地，开创电影行业的新纪元…或者一败涂地。毕竟电影行业就是这样 – 成者为王败者为寇。佳片相约—电影制片厂大亨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576280/extras/dc15423d4cf100062586e04f27c11853.poster.avif?t=1728902403\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576280/extras/dc15423d4cf100062586e04f27c11853.webm?t=1728902403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>初生牛犊 </strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验时代的沉淀 – 从八十年代的一个小工作室干起，拍摄短片，品味票房的甜美。生意兴隆，自然就能扩张，拍摄更好的电影，签约更多的艺人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>舍我其谁</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发挥才智，击败同行竞争者；明察秋毫，找到下一个票房热点。赢得各路奖项，占领市场蛋糕，成为好莱坞有史以来最成功的片厂！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>神片出世</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想怎么拍就怎么拍 – 从十余种大类中选择，并加以扣人心弦的故事。不论是间谍片，浪漫剧，血浆恐怖还是标新原创都手到擒来。在演员、道具特效和场景间进行分配决策，拍出影史经典，成为电影教父。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576280/extras/7f2d1d62caa3a81b99a734481cffb425.avif?t=1728902403\" width=610 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>操盘圣手</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组成终极全明星阵容 – 雇佣导演与编剧，培养他们的创意以及技能，确保创作产出。优秀的团队能让影院坐满顾客，而导演则负责掌舵于怒涛。将小演员栽培成大明星，或者不出名就坐冷板凳，您是老板，您说了算！</p>",
